This config has an identical CONFIG_ID to config_4_attribute_list, which isn't valid.

It's also the same in every other attribute except EGL_NATIVE_VISUAL_ID. How do clients differentiate between these two (i.e. how do they know which one to pick), considering that the GGL_PIXEL_FORMAT enum is private to libagl and meaningless to clients?

