We did copy config_4_attribute_list with an intention of creating a custom BGRA_8888 EGL_NATIVE_VISUAL_ID and this CONFIG_ID mixup is indeed an oversight. Thanks for pointing that out, we will fix that.

 > How do clients differentiate between these
